{"type":"message","id":"ddc48e48","parentId":"12565d6f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:59:34.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm a general-purpose assistant with access to a bunch of tools. Here's the gist:\n\n**Core stuff:**\n- Read/write files, run shell commands\n- Search the web, browse websites\n- Spawn coding agents (Codex, Claude Code, etc.) for bigger tasks\n\n**Integrations:**\n- **Feishu/Lark** — calendars, docs, tasks, spreadsheets, group chats, messages\n- **WeCom** — contacts, meetings, schedules, docs, smart sheets\n- **QQ Bot** — reminders\n- **Discord/Telegram/WhatsApp/etc.** — messaging (if connected)\n\n**Skills I can use:**\n- Weather lookups\n- Browser automation\n- Web search (SearXNG)\n- And more — there's a whole skill system I can pull from\n\n**Practical examples:**\n- \"Check my calendar for tomorrow\"\n- \"Create a spreadsheet to track expenses\"\n- \"Search for recent news on AI\"\n- \"Set a reminder in 2 hours\"\n- \"Spawn a coding agent to build a Python script\"\n\nWhat are you working on? I can probably help with it."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774843163786}}
