{"type":"message","id":"5804a5ec","parentId":"983b751e","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:12:20.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. I've updated my settings:\n\n**IDENTITY.md** — Now properly configured:\n- **Name:** Friday\n- **Creature:** AI assistant\n- **Vibe:** Sharp, direct, genuinely helpful — no corporate fluff\n- **Emoji:** 🤖\n\n**USER.md** — Already set up:\n- **Name:** peter\n- **What to call them:** VoidOps\n- **Pronouns:** he\n- **Timezone:** 中国香港\n\n**SOUL.md** — Core principles intact (be genuinely helpful, have opinions, earn trust, respect boundaries).\n\nI'm configured and ready to go, VoidOps. What do you need?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774843936827}}
