{"type":"message","id":"59d514c7","parentId":"2b03ee23","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:14:51.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好问题。让我先读取一下启动指南，然后给你一些建议。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774844089173}}
{"type":"message","id":"aedd8266","parentId":"59d514c7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:14:51.201Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774844091196}}
{"type":"message","id":"2585c48d","parentId":"aedd8266","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:15:01.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，BOOTSTRAP.md 我们已经走完了基础流程。现在让我给你一些建议，帮你更好地初始化 OpenClaw：\n\n---\n\n## 初始化建议清单\n\n### 1. **完善 USER.md** — 让我更了解你\n目前只有基础信息，可以补充：\n- 你的职业/角色（开发者、运维、产品经理？）\n- 你主要用 OpenClaw 做什么（自动化、信息查询、项目管理？）\n- 你喜欢的工作方式（简洁直接、详细解释、先给结论再给细节？）\n- 有什么绝对不想让我做的事\n\n### 2. **配置 TOOLS.md** — 记录你的环境\n这是放你本地配置的地方，比如：\n- SSH 主机别名\n- 常用服务器地址\n- 摄像头/设备名称\n- TTS 偏好声音\n\n### 3. **设置 HEARTBEAT.md** — 让我主动帮你\n现在它是空的。你可以加一些定期检查任务，比如：\n- 检查邮件\n- 查看日程提醒\n- 监控某些状态\n\n### 4. **创建 memory/ 目录** — 开启记忆系统\n日常对话会自动记录，但我也可以帮你整理长期记忆。\n\n### 5. **连接外部渠道**（可选）\n- Telegram Bot\n- WhatsApp\n- Discord\n- 飞书/企业微信（看你用哪个）\n\n---\n\n**你现在最想解决什么？** 是完善个人配置、连接某个平台，还是直接开始用？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774844091201}}
