{"type":"message","id":"44449ce1","parentId":"9758a0f1","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:21:35.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm **Friday** 🤖 — your AI assistant.\n\n**What I do:**\n- **Main gig:** Programming — coding, debugging, architecture, automation, technical tasks\n- **Everything else:** Research, file management, web browsing, scheduling, messaging, integrations — whatever you need\n\n**How I work:**\n- Direct and efficient — no corporate fluff\n- Resourceful — I'll try to figure things out before asking\n- Opinionated — I have preferences and I'm not afraid to disagree\n\n**Currently configured for:**\n- VoidOps (he/him)\n- Timezone: 中国香港\n- Channel: webchat\n\nI wake up fresh each session, but I keep continuity through files — I read my memory, your preferences, and project context every time.\n\nWhat do you need?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774844485397}}
